.hero-unit
  %h1 Leucurus
  %p Relationship management for community organizers.

  %a{class: "btn btn-primary btn-large"} Learn more

.row-fluid
  .span4
    %h4 Build Relationships
    %p
      Community organizers need help building relationships around shared
      values.  Leucurus helps you build strong relationships by helping keeping
      track of and understanding how a relationship has progressed and what the
      next steps are.

  .span4
    %h4 Mobilize Relationships
    %p
      Community organizers need help mobilizing relationships into action.
      Leucurus helps you keep track of what needs to get done, who is doing
      what, and what skills, assets, and interests your team has.

  .span4
    %h4 Share Relationships
    %p
      Community organizers need help sharing rich information about
      relationships with others.  Leucurus helps you share and pass off strong
      relationships with ease by providing robust privacy and sharing controls
      along with rich data.
